### 3.1 `atomic-asx-blocks.css`

This is a small, reusable atomic CSS sheet that matches the docs’ visual language and can be reused in other OS surfaces.

```css
/* atomic-asx-blocks.css */
/* Core palette */
:root {
  --ax-bg: #020308;
  --ax-bg-panel: #070b12;
  --ax-border: #16f2aa;
